'''''T-Force''''' was the designation given to a group of four [[Alderaanian/Legends|Alderaanian]] [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. They were heading for Alderaan carrying [[Power generator/Legends|power generators]] (''T-Force 1''), base equipment (''T-Force 3'') and general supplies (''T-Force 2'' and ''T-Force 4'') when the ''Tantive IV'' [[Death Star plans delivery|hid]] among the convoy to avoid [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] attention on its way to deliver the recently acquired [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]] plans to Alderaan.

